    <item>
      <title>尽管美联储大幅降息，日元兑美元汇率仍跌至 145</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/yen-weakens-to-145-against-dollar-despite-jumbo-fed-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元跌至9月初以来的最低水平，因为即使美联储降息后，收益率差距缩小的速度仍不确定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/yen-weakens-to-145-against-dollar-despite-jumbo-fed-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 04:10:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新世界考虑更换亿万富翁继承人担任首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/new-world-weighs-replacing-billionaire-heir-cheng-as-ceo-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新世界发展公司在彭博社报道该公司正考虑更换第三代继承人郑志刚担任首席执行官后，该公司暂停了在香港的股票交易。此前，该公司因减记导致 20 年来首次出现年度亏损。彭博社企业集团和媒体记者 Shirley Zhao 在“彭博社：中国秀”节目中与 Yvonne Man 讨论了相关细节。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/new-world-weighs-replacing-billionaire-heir-cheng-as-ceo-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 04:07:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>寒流袭击南部，澳大利亚小麦作物再遭打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/australia-wheat-crop-dealt-another-blow-as-cold-snap-hits-south</link>
      <description><![CDATA[严重霜冻威胁到澳大利亚南部和东南部的农田，预计这些地区的小麦产量将占该国小麦总产量的 10% 以上，这加剧了人们对西部地区干旱的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/australia-wheat-crop-dealt-another-blow-as-cold-snap-hits-south</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 04:05:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>预知未来并不会让你赚钱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-09-26/knowing-the-future-won-t-make-you-money</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即使交易员已经知道明天的消息，他们仍然可能表现不佳。真正重要的是他们下注多少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-09-26/knowing-the-future-won-t-make-you-money</guid>
