    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的 Jewell 表示，股票可以应对盈利下调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/blackrock-s-jewell-says-stocks-can-cope-with-earnings-downgrades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司的海伦·朱厄尔 (Helen Jewell) 表示，尽管今年剩余时间全球企业盈利预期看似乐观，但股市目前可能能够吸收适度的下调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/blackrock-s-jewell-says-stocks-can-cope-with-earnings-downgrades</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚央行认为林吉特将获得“持久支持”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/malaysia-s-central-bank-sees-enduring-support-for-ringgit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚央行表示，鉴于马来西亚良好的经济前景和改革，林吉特的涨势可能持续下去。本周，林吉特攀升至三年来的最高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/malaysia-s-central-bank-sees-enduring-support-for-ringgit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 09:02:20 GMT</pubDate>
